uk.co.strangeskies.reflection.codegen

Interface AnnotatedSignature<S extends AnnotatedSignature<S>>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - a self-bound over the type of the implementing class
    All Superinterfaces:
    Signature<S>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ParameterizedSignature<S>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClassSignature, ConstructorSignature, ExecutableSignature, FieldSignature, MemberSignature, MethodSignature, ParameterSignature, TypeVariableSignature

    public interface AnnotatedSignature<S extends AnnotatedSignature<S>>
extends Signature<S>
    An base type for any source declaration objects which are annotated. Implementations should be immutable.

    • Method Detail

      • getAnnotations

        Stream<? extends Annotation> getAnnotations()
        Returns:
        the annotations on this declaration

      • withAnnotations

        default S withAnnotations(Annotation... annotations)
        Derive a version of this declaration with the given annotations. Users should take care not to specify annotations which could not be applied to the declaration due to their Target, as there is no validation of applicability.

        Annotations already present on the receiving declaration will be replaced rather than appended.

        Parameters:
        annotations - the annotations with which to annotate this declaration
        Returns:
        a new declaration of the same type, and with the same content, but with the given annotations

      • withAnnotations

        S withAnnotations(Collection<? extends Annotation> annotations)
        Derive a version of this declaration with the given annotations. Users should take care not to specify annotations which could not be applied to the declaration due to their Target, as there is no validation of applicability.

        Annotations already present on the receiving declaration will be replaced rather than appended.

        Parameters:
        annotations - the annotations with which to annotate this declaration
        Returns:
        a new declaration of the same type, and with the same content, but with the given annotations
